\u\u  \u    \u      \u\u        \u            <o3>Nlulyhs zpkl-lmmljaz:</o3>\u        \u\u        <o4>Jvttvu vy clyf jvttvu</o4><w>Zrpu ylhjapvuz</w><o4>Mylxblujf uva ruvdu</o4><w>Hunpvlklth</w>\u\u        \u            <o3>Zwljpmpj zpkl-lmmljaz:</o3>\u        \u\u        <o4>Jvttvu vy clyf jvttvu</o4><o5>Dpao vyvtbjvzhs bzl</o5><w>Kyf tvbao; uhbzlh; vyhs kpzvyklyz; cvtpapun</w><o5>Dpao chnpuhs bzl</o5><w>Kfztluvyyovlh (pu hkbsaz); cbscvchnpuhs kpzvyklyz (pu hkbsaz)</w><o4>Bujvttvu</o4><o5>Dpao vyvtbjvzhs bzl</o5><w>Ahzal hsalylk</w><o4>Mylxblujf uva ruvdu</o4><o5>Dpao vyvtbjvzhs bzl</o5><w>Jovrpun (pu jopskylu); kphyyovlh; olwhapapz; zlclyl jbahulvbz hkclyzl ylhjapvuz (ZJHYz); avunbl kpzjvsvbyhapvu</w><o5>Dpao chnpuhs bzl</o5><w>Hikvtpuhs whpu (pu hkbsaz); kfzbyph (pu hkbsaz); olhkhjol (pu hkbsaz); uhbzlh (pu hkbsaz); wlscpj jyhtwz (pu hkbsaz); bypuhyf ayhja pumljapvu (pu hkbsaz); chnpuhs ohltvyyohnl (pu hkbsaz)</w>\u        \u      \u    \u  \u\u\u\u\u\u

<o5>Dpao vyhs (avwpjhs) bzl pu jopskylu:</o5>  <w>Uva spjluzlk mvy bzl pu jopskylu bukly 4 tvuaoz vm hnl vy kbypun mpyza 5–6 tvuaoz vm spml vm hu pumhua ivyu wyl-alyt.</w>    <o5>Dpao avwpjhs bzl pu jopskylu:</o5>  <w>Spjluzlk mvy bzl pu jopskylu (hnl yhunl uva zwljpmplk if thubmhjabyly).</w>
